title Aegis Data and Integrations Architecture

direction right

Domain Services [icon: layers, color: blue] {
  Incident Service [icon: activity]
  Patient Service [icon: heart]
  Provider Service [icon: building]
  Insurance Service [icon: shield]
  Routing Service [icon: navigation]
  Assessment Service [icon: clipboard]
}

AI and Orchestration [icon: cpu, color: indigo] {
  Orchestrator Service [icon: workflow]
  Emergency Triage Agent [icon: alert-circle]
  Dispatch Agent [icon: truck]
  RAG Service [icon: search]
  Search Client [icon: azure-cognitive-search]
  Kernel Engine [icon: terminal, label: "Semantic Kernel"]
}

Data Repositories [icon: database, color: green] {
  Incident Repository [icon: database]
  Decision Trace Repository [icon: database]
  Patient Repository [icon: database]
  Provider Repository [icon: database]
  Insurance Repository [icon: database]
  Zone Clinic Ambulance Repositories [icon: database, label: "Zone/Clinic/Ambulance Repos"]
}

Azure and External Integrations [icon: cloud, color: cyan] {
  Azure OpenAI [icon: azure-openai]
  Azure AI Search Index [icon: azure-cognitive-search]
  Azure Maps [icon: azure-maps-accounts]
  Provider External API [icon: globe]
  Insurance External API [icon: globe]
}

Governance [icon: eye, color: purple] {
  Observability Service [icon: activity]
  Error Handler [icon: alert-triangle]
  Azure Monitor [icon: azure-monitor]
  Application Insights [icon: azure-application-insights]
}

Incident Service > Incident Repository: read/write
Patient Service > Patient Repository: read/write
Provider Service > Provider Repository: read/write
Insurance Service > Insurance Repository: read/write
Routing Service > Zone Clinic Ambulance Repositories: read/write
Assessment Service > Incident Repository: read/write

Orchestrator Service > Emergency Triage Agent: reasoning
Orchestrator Service > Dispatch Agent: reasoning
Orchestrator Service > RAG Service: retrieve context
Orchestrator Service > Kernel Engine: prompt execution
Orchestrator Service > Decision Trace Repository: audit trail
Orchestrator Service > Incident Service: persist updates

RAG Service > Search Client: retrieve context
Search Client > Azure AI Search Index: retrieve context
Kernel Engine > Azure OpenAI: reasoning
Emergency Triage Agent > Azure OpenAI: reasoning
Dispatch Agent > Azure Maps: route calculation
Routing Service > Azure Maps: route calculation

Provider Service > Provider External API: external validation
Insurance Service > Insurance External API: external validation
Provider External API > Provider Service: normalized response
Insurance External API > Insurance Service: normalized response

Incident Service > Orchestrator Service: feedback loop

Incident Service --> Observability Service: trace/log
Patient Service --> Observability Service: trace/log
Provider Service --> Observability Service: trace/log
Insurance Service --> Observability Service: trace/log
Orchestrator Service --> Observability Service: trace/log
Observability Service > Azure Monitor: telemetry
Azure Monitor > Application Insights: telemetry
Error Handler > Application Insights: trace/log

legend {
  [connection: ">", label: "Direct flow"]
  [connection: "-->", label: "Telemetry / async"]
}
